            <title><![CDATA[习近平：对东北振兴充满信心]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/img-1660711522892364b300197bbde0eb15d1579cffe29a7b0d5662098c7d1fd12f4de24a91fadc0.jpg?VersionId=UE.3Z2MAlJ0y1tfQ29eSGtXeb.ujoIL8&amp;itok=JFiA9apm" title="中国国家主席习近平星期二在辽宁省锦州市考察时与市民交流。（新华社微博）" alt="中国国家主席习近平星期二在辽宁省锦州市考察时与市民交流。（新华社微博）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/img-1660711522892364b300197bbde0eb15d1579cffe29a7b0d5662098c7d1fd12f4de24a91fadc0.jpg?VersionId=UE.3Z2MAlJ0y1tfQ29eSGtXeb.ujoIL8&amp;itok=JFiA9apm" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
